Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:45.50,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.667,478)}{\fad(750,500)}Zou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:45.50,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\fad(279,0)\pos(640,568)}DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\fad(485,0)\pos(640,548)}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não há nenhuma lista de contrabando.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas há evidências claras\N de que foi roubada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Foi o que pensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,As armas que ficaram no\N porto comercial subterrâneo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...foram roubadas após o incidente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Era uma grande quantidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:09.31,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150\fad(523,0)\pos(640,475)}CIPHER POL "AEGIS" ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Foi obra de alguma organização.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A Marinha também\N fez escândalo por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi o Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Não poderia ter sido mais ninguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Volte já.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.03,Main,,0,0,0,,São uns caras irritantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...assim como você.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não exagere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde você vai agora, Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Este é o país da tragédia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:48.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fios escuros pendurados um após o outro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Contêm as lágrimas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...das numerosas tragédias\N que lhes ocorreram e entoam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:03.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...a sonora melodia das palmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fecha-se a cortina de um palco sombrio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...no qual houve um longo período\N de tristeza e sem aplausos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...enquanto palavras de\N sinceridade chegam a todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:34.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,O rei voltou, trazendo a paz\N e tudo transcorre tranquilamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Tenho uma proposta a fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh, obrigado pela apresentação.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou Gancho, o Chefe Tonta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ao meu lado está minha filha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou Mansherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Que fofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Você quer que façamos isso, Leo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Este ano é o Reverie,\N a reunião mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Será em breve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos os países já\N começaram a se preparar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca disse que virá esta\N tarde para preparar a comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,E Kyros?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Virão juntos, é claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bom, que bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Toda a família se reunirá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...depois de tanto tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:48.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Os viajantes que visitarem este país\N ficarão surpresos com uma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dá presunto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, bem-vindas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca, Mansherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Que se misturam com a cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...e convivem com total\N naturalidade com os humanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não construímos as moradias.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, não, esta é\N nossa prioridade máxima!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pelos encantadores anões.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:27.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Este é o país do amor, da paixão e das fadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,As estátuas de bronze vêm primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Quando terminarmos\N esta tarefa de escolta,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}viajarei sem rumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:48.41,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(530,0)\pos(640,542)}FROTA DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você vai viajar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Enquanto não pegar as cabeças de\N Chapéu de Palha e de Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,não posso entrar em nenhuma base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito tolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você se desculpar, Sakazuki\N recuperará sua honra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque eu também\N tenho minha própria honra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,725)}Fujitora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,É um idiota, Tsuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Era a última chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele tivesse me ajudado e nós\N tivéssemos lidado com esses pirralhos,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.34,Main,,0,0,0,,isso não teria acontecido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu tinha as rédeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,As rédeas dos monstros do mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Não deveriam ter me derrotado.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles se arrependerão.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare de dizer coisas tão patéticas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,O "se" não existe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.84,Main,,0,0,0,,O mundo não se baseia em caprichos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,A única realidade é esta:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Você perdeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Caramba, não sou páreo para você.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Entre criminosos, nos entendemos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Como será o mundo dos\N piratas de agora em diante?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou mudar a pergunta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você acha que os monstros, que tiveram suas correntes cortadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...e perderam sua comida, farão?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que no mar há alguém\N que está acima dos outros?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é o rei deste mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Um dos Yonkou,\N os imperadores do mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(612,0)}Ou um dos Shichibukai que se viram\N com astúcia para sobreviver neste mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(441,0)}Ou um piratinha da pior geração?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,A Marinha, o exército da justiça,\N é quem governa os mares!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,E também o Exército Revolucionário,\N que possui a vontade das massas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,762)}tem homens fortes diante dos quais\N não se pode baixar a guarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,O clã dos D que está\N escondido na história...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde e quando aparecerá?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem apoiará quem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem trairá quem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga aos Tenryuubito de Mary Geoise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...que eles cairão de onde estão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Já se passaram vinte e cinco anos desde que Gold Roger\N conquistou o Grand Line pela primeira vez na história.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Barba Branca, seu velho inimigo,\N não se sentou no trono...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...e governou de pé diante dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas e agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,O número de piratas está aumentando...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...e há um trono vazio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Você entende, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Está prestes a começar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:21.48,Main,,0,0,0,,O maior conflito pela hegemonia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...na história da pirataria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,O mastro está pegando fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos para Impel Down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, tragam-me o jornal diariamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Assim não ficarei entediado.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,São quatro navios de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas têm pessoas muito perigosas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que querem destruir um país?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,É incrível que tomem tantas\N medidas para um simples transporte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Como era de esperar de Doflamingo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,É impossível recuperar Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Capitão Jack, voltamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro que vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos você acha que eu sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.59,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\\pos(1072,395)}{\fad(500,500)} POR OUTRO LADO,\N LUFFY E SUA TRIPULAÇÃO{PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.78,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(637.333,483.667)}{\fad(250,500)}NAVIO DO BARTO CLUB\N"GOING LUFFY-SENPAI" {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Estão loucos? {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que parece que Luffy está\N mais neste navio do que no nosso?! {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em ouvir isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é um elogio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,E agora, o que mais nos emociona é...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...que para onde aponta esta Vivre Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.04,Secondary,,0,0,0,,...que para onde aponta esta Vivre Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,...está o verdadeiro Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.74,Secondary,,0,0,0,,...está o verdadeiro Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado por\N embarcar neste navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Não consigo ver seu rosto,\N está muito brilhante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também não!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,São todos iguais?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, que bom que\N Sabo fez uma Vivre Card meu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.26,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)}E eu fiz uma Vivre Card\N de Luffy por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Oh, quando foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,269)}Vou pegar um pedaço.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Como era de esperar de\N Sabo, meu grande senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é forte e atencioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pessoa incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:45.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2025,0)}Não serei seu subordinado,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,mas vou levar por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.64,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Nós também vamos pegar um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Bem, aqui nos despedimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:58.57,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos ver de novo, chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:05.62,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1976)}Nos vemos, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, que banquete divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Gostei deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo, vamos nos apressar para ir a Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Para quem você acha que está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Conto com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,À velocidade máxima para Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.30,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que Sanji e os outros\N chegaram em segurança à ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami estava com eles, então com certeza não houve problemas com a navegação,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,mas o que terá acontecido com \No navio da Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou preocupada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que nossas recompensas aumentaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã? Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, vocês não sabiam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, os pôsteres de recompensa \Nestão no meu quarto, entrem, entrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Entrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.59,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Entrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, vou dar uma olhada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,O seu eu joguei fora, mas aumentou para 500 milhões.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não ligo para o valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, olhem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Estão emoldurados?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Os autógrafos que vocês \Nme deram antes estão aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, primeiro o do \NChapéu de Palha Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(808,130)}YO {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(1070,410)}PARA BARTOLOMEO\N USOPP {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(330,385)}ESPADA {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(230,620)}PARA MEU IRMÃO \NFRANKY {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\pos(1010,600)}NICO ROBIN {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Sua recompensa é de\N 500 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:26.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}500 milhões, incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.03,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(521,0)\pos(420,510)}CHAPÉU DE PALHA LUFFY\NRECOMPENSA: 500 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora o Caçador de\N Piratas, Zoro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}320 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:36.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(524,0)\pos(420,510)}CAÇADOR DE PIRATAS, ZORO\NRECOMPENSA: 320 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei, você tem saquê?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nico Robin-senpai, a Filha do Demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}130 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.84,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(522,0)\pos(870,512)}NICO ROBIN, A FILHA DO DEMÔNIO \N RECOMPENSA: 130 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, não, aumentou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Franky-senpai, o Homem de Ferro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}94 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Foi perto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:55.81,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(524,0)\pos(395,510)}FRANKY, O HOMEM DE FERRO\NRECOMPENSA: 94 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Além disso, a foto é do Franky Shogun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Deus Usopp-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,729)}200 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(522,0)\pos(885,512)}DEUS USOPP\N RECOMPENSA: 200 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não tenho o rosto coberto e \Né uma quantia enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão atrás de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas isso me deixa feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não gostei da foto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, não enche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que sua recompensa aumentou tanto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Até meu companheiro quer me matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou o único que não \Npassou dos cem milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Que frustrante!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Espera, espera! Olhe bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem a Nami e os outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sanji-senpai, Perna Negra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}177 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.68,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(522,0)\pos(430,512)}SANJI, PERNA NEGRA\NRECOMPENSA: 177 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, o pôster do Sanji já \Nnão tem um retrato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Que chato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,O anterior era mais engraçado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nami-senpai, a Gata Ladra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}66 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:48.15,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(487,0)\pos(910,512)}NAMI, A GATA LADRA\NRECOMPENSA: 66 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Quando tiraram essa foto dela?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chopper-senpai, o Amante \Ndo Algodão Doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}100 berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.20,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(274,0)\pos(420,512)}CHOPPER, O AMANTE DO ALGODÃO DOCE\NRECOMPENSA: 100 BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}N-Não sei o que dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Brook-senpai, Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}83 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.09,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fscx150\fscy150\fad(522,0)\pos(870,512)}BROOK, SOUL KING\N RECOMPENSA: 83 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mas é um pôster do seu show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Além das pessoas que\N participaram deste incidente...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,...e que se destacaram por mostrar sua periculosidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,todos tiveram um aumento de 50 milhões na recompensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,As nossas também \Naumentaram cinquenta milhões.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...olhem isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Quanto ao Sanji-senpai, Perna Negra,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,seu pôster e o aumento da\N recompensa são estranhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Só vivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,É granizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,São enormes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Fizeram um buraco no convés!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai e companhia!{\i1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Entrem lá dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos te ajudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde estamos indo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é o navegador de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Nos dê instruções!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, não temos navegador porque \Ncostumávamos ficar em terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos no Novo Mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Alô, vovó?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou eu, Gambia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Está caindo um granizo enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando estamos em apuros, chamamos \Nnossa avó, que está na cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Já entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela dá conselhos precisos sobre o mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, já entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Não podemos tirar o chiclete\N colado no casco, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, sempre dá problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.79,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim, sempre dá problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Envolvam o granizo em pano \Ne resfriem o chiclete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Saiu surpreendentemente fácil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Não precisamos desse tipo de sabedoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas mesmo assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem, funcionou!{Não separo}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela diz para colocarmos \Naçúcar no machucado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Chega dessa sabedoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O navio vai afundar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami, nos ajude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,De tantos navios para escolher, \Nescolhemos o errado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos escolha a não ser fazer algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ao menos tivéssemos o equipamento do Sunny...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Que animado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,E a sua barreira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, é que a vovó diz que...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...se desafiarmos a natureza, Deus nos castigará.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você tem medo, volte para a terra firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão falando sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ter a tripulação do Chapéu\N de Palha, que não teme a Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,conosco é como ter a ajuda de mil homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Agradecemos muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.89,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Agradecemos muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Como diabos vocês sobreviveram tanto tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.35,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ajudem vocês também!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Os Piratas A. O. que pertenciam aos \NPiratas de Barba Branca foram aniquilados.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:36.99,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(900,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}QUARTEL-GENERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}De novo ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, Edward Weevil, membro dos Shichibukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:46.12,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,485)\fad(500,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}ALMIRANTE DO QUARTEL-\NGERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:46.12,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}KIZARU (BORSALINO)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Quantos capitães aliados de Barba Branca...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...foram derrotados até agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Dezesseis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Como nos outros casos, foram derrotados...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...junto com a cidade após uma discussão.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Houve cerca de seiscentas baixas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Por onde ele passa, os civis \Nsempre sofrem grandes danos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sendo um Shichibukai, não \Npodemos ignorar isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Que problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele se diz o filho biológico \Nde Edward Newgate, Barba Branca,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,e é poderoso, mas muitos não acreditam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, para nós não importa se ele é ou não.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Independentemente da relação \Nbiológica, ele tem mérito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:32.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Como pirata, ele é extremamente poderoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Igual ao Barba Branca quando era jovem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Embora apenas em força.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Uma semana depois de partir de Dressrosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem muita neblina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Não dá para ver nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês ficam enjoados demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,E se dizem piratas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiclete, chiclete...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A vovó diz que com chiclete \Na gente se sente melhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,É por isso que tem chiclete \Ncolado por todo o navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Que interessante!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Vejo algo às duas horas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Na densa neblina,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,tem uma montanha ou um monstro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Não existe monstro que possa ser\N confundido com uma montanha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ele se move devagar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Você só está enjoado, maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Se é uma montanha que se move, vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiota, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Por enquanto,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,vamos sair desse labirinto de neblina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos bater em um recife e virar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Espera, Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Deus, você diz?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Você me faz corar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,O homem dos duzentos \Nmilhões está corando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Com certeza, caras do nível \Ndos almirantes sabem de você.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Olha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A Vivre Card aponta para aquilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, seu companheiro está lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Usopp, você está pálido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Quer um chiclete?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu estava evitando a realidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...que Zou é uma ilha que impede invasões\N graças a uma densa neblina e uma corrente contrária.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem vento contrário também!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Recolham as velas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos chegar remando!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.96,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,E essa resposta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa é a ilha chamada Zou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, é estranha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Dêem meia-volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, aqui está bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas é um elefante!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, Zou é o nome da terra que\N prospera nas costas de um elefante gigante.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está vivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não para de se mover, então \Nnão fica no mesmo lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma ilha fantasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se pode chegar aqui com Log Poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que venho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele estar de costas para nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...significa que Perna Negra e companhia podem ter chegado muito antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Estávamos perseguindo um \Nelefante que estava se afastando.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para atracar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Você pode nos dar comida?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que para você?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Você pode dar para o Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele pode levar tudo o que tem no depósito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Então isso é Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Então no exterior há \Ntodo tipo de coisas estranhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que Momonosuke está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouvi dizer que em Zou há uma \Ntribo que odeia humanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, a tribo Mink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que eles não deixam humanos se aproximarem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...e que sua história remonta a mil anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:16.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Mil anos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Nas costas do elefante?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, esse elefante vive há mil anos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã? Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Não me digam que...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Então esse é...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse é...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,...o grande navio que carrega a \Nsagrada Tripulação do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Thousand Sunny-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!{Não sei se deveria separar aqui}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:15.44,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Não o adorem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles chegaram a Zou sem errar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que fugiram dos \Nsubordinados da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há danos aparentes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,E como se chamava aquele cara do gás?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Senpai, se apressem e atravessem...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde eles foram?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles já estão atravessando!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:45.93,Main,,0,0,0,,E os outros?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que não estão aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:49.65,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:51.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que todos desembarcaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, tenham cuidado, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também vem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisam de mais alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu queria segui-los...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,...e ver todas as estrelas...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...dos Chapéus de Palha\N com meus próprios olhos,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,mas não posso me intrometer\N nas aventuras dos meus deuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Nosso medidor de felicidade \Njá está no máximo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Da próxima vez que nos vermos,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,teremos habilidades dignas\N de serem consideradas...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...como as dos membros dos Chapéus de Palha! {subordinados por membros?, em inglês é subordinados e faz mais sentido}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Se então pudermos ser úteis,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:32.61,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(433,0)}GOTEJOS DIVINOS (AUTÓGRAFOS)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,queremos os quatro gotejos \Ndivinos dos senpai restantes!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Se conseguirmos, será \Num imenso privilégio!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma minhoca?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.48,0:24:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma cobra, não?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem pernas, é uma lagartixa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.37,0:24:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles me ignoram!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Completamente ignorado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas mesmo assim estou feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:51.88,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Que alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, terminei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.98,0:25:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.54,0:25:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma cobra, não?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,É... uma cobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Apareça, dragão escalador!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.48,0:25:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragão?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragão...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.44,0:25:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Dragão...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.42,0:25:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Apareceu uma criatura patética!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.26,0:26:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,É olho por olho.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:05.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Que fofo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.19,0:26:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, todos segurem-se nas costas dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.38,0:26:17.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não vai voar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.90,0:26:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.63,0:26:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.38,0:26:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, dragão!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Quantos quilômetros faltam para o topo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.78,0:26:36.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Não dá para ver onde termina essa perna!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.08,0:26:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que realmente há um país lá em cima?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.36,0:26:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.91,0:26:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,A Vivre Card aponta para cima.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.01,0:26:42.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.72,0:26:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, dragão!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.58,0:26:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Até mais, Lomeo e companhia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.96,0:26:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por nos trazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.16,0:26:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.18,0:26:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Ele disse meu nome?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que ele \Nme chama pelo nome!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.60,0:27:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz por você, chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.48,0:27:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Igualmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.76,0:27:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.62,0:27:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, tenham cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês também!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.34,0:27:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.38,0:27:19.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:21.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Fique bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.00,0:27:30.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,E assim, eles seguem para o topo \Nde Zou, a ilha fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:47.35,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,476)\fad(433,0)}GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:47.35,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,0)}BALTIGO - QUARTEL-GERAL DOS REVOLUCIONÁRIOS
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.32,0:27:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragon-san!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.76,0:27:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Os insurgentes estão ganhando em todo o mundo!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.47,0:27:53.61,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(433,511)}COMANDANTE-GERAL DO\N EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.47,0:27:53.61,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,511)}MONKEY D. DRAGON
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.80,0:27:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,O impacto da queda da\N Família Donquixote foi enorme.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.28,0:27:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos esses países...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.06,0:27:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...estavam envolvidos no tráfico de armas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.82,0:27:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,O progresso da guerra mudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.84,0:28:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas diga a eles para não deixarem \Nque as vitórias os façam vacilar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.39,0:28:06.14,Main,,0,0,0,,O Governo Mundial não ficará \Nde braços cruzados!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O Cipher Pol foi reforçado \Nnos últimos anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.92,0:28:11.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga a eles para terem muito cuidado.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.06,0:28:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:15.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.40,0:28:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,As armas que trouxemos de Dressrosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.82,0:28:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,...continham um mineral especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Mineral?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.55,0:28:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Você conhece o minério de ferro alcoólico?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:30.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Como é raro e poucas nações o produzem,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.68,0:28:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,talvez possamos descobrir quem está \Npor trás da fabricação dessas armas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, isso são boas notícias.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.62,0:28:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.82,0:28:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Os companheiros que desapareceram \Nem Dressrosa também voltaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.61,0:28:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles fizeram um trabalho esplêndido.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.64,0:28:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, não foi tanto assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.48,0:28:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Estavam Sabo-kun e Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.84,0:28:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Como estava Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.62,0:28:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, o boato de que ela havia sido \Ncapturada em Sabaody era falso.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.50,0:28:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:28:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-san estava muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.29,0:28:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Como se...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.58,0:28:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não vai perguntar sobre Luffy-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, já ouvi demais sobre ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.52,0:29:06.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sabo-kun contou para você.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.76,0:29:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A propósito, Koala...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos da sua força.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Da sua força?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.18,0:29:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Chame todos os líderes do \NExército Revolucionário de todo o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.38,0:29:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.60,0:29:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.32,0:29:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele quer reunir essas grandes \Npersonalidades de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.16,0:29:32.04,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(433,467)}EM ALGUM MAR DO NOVO MUNDO
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Lafitte falando.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.47,0:29:45.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Falando...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.50,0:29:47.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...urgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.26,0:29:51.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.50,0:29:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,É você, hein?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.85,0:29:58.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(433,0)}COMANDANTE DA QUINTA DIVISÃO DOS PIRATAS DO YONKOU BARBA NEGRA
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.85,0:29:58.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,0)}LAFFITE, O COMISSÁRIO DEMONÍACO
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.42,0:29:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Fomos a Dressrosa, mas você não estava lá.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:58.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sim, desculpe.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.83,0:30:02.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Não pude me comunicar porque \Nestava praticamente inconsciente.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.93,0:30:08.76,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(433,0)}COMANDANTE DA SEGUNDA DIVISÃO DOS PIRATAS DO YONKOU BARBA NEGRA
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.93,0:30:08.76,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,0)}SHIRYU DA CHUVA
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.10,0:30:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa, aquele desgraçado estava vivo?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.76,0:30:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde você esteve?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.72,0:30:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tudo está branco...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.58,0:30:19.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Em uma ilha completamente branca.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.16,0:30:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Estive escondido no fundo de um navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.59,0:30:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga ao Capitão Teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.22,0:30:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...que se invadirmos aqui, \Nconseguiremos uma grande quantidade de armas!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.34,0:30:33.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,É Major Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.89,0:30:35.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes tenho que te dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.54,0:30:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Traga Doc Q também!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.04,0:30:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou gravemente ferido e \Nà beira da morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.58,0:30:41.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:42.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Já nos diga!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:43.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Onde fica isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.64,0:30:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sei o nome da ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.66,0:30:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,É um lugar desconhecido para todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.13,0:30:53.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sigam minha Vivre Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.12,0:30:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui estão Dragon e aquele odioso Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.42,0:31:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Encontrei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Quartel-General \Ndo Exército Revolucionário!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.23,0:31:28.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(433,0)}EM CERTA ILHA
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.23,0:31:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos dizem a mesma bobagem!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.24,0:31:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Não param de dizer a mesma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.58,0:31:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Que os únicos filhos de Barba Branca\N são os Piratas do Barba Branca!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.25,0:31:48.76,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,435)\fad(433,0)}MEMBRO DO OUKA SHICHIBUKAI, O \NAUTOPROCLAMADO "BARBA BRANCA JR." - EDWARD WEEVIL
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.25,0:31:48.76,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,713)\fad(433,0)}RECOMPENSA ANTERIOR: 480 MILHÕES
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Mamãe!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.90,0:31:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu sou o filho do Barba Branca, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:48.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Minha barba é branca!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo, querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.60,0:31:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas do Barba Branca não são \Nmais que uma família falsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.22,0:32:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é o único filho biológico de Barba Branca, o pirata mais forte do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.62,0:32:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.89,0:32:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,E eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:09.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,485)\fad(433,0)}MÃE DE WEEVIL E A AUTOPROCLAMADA\N "AMANTE DE BARBA BRANCA"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:09.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,0)}MISS BAKKIN
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.80,0:32:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...sou a mulher que Barba Branca amou.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.72,0:32:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Então seja forte, querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.62,0:32:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Está doendo, mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.86,0:32:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.08,0:32:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.92,0:32:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,É um espelho?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.96,0:32:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, é uma foto do Barba Branca!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.88,0:32:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, pensei que fosse um espelho.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês se parecem muito, é \Nimpossível que você não seja filho dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.98,0:32:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você pode ser tão idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.76,0:32:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, desculpe, mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.62,0:32:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu te perdoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.52,0:32:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque eu te amo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.42,0:32:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.31,0:32:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.66,0:32:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Faça o que tem que fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.70,0:32:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.50,0:32:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Esqueci.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.55,0:33:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Você começará procurando os remanescentes dos Piratas do Barba Branca, começando por Marco, a Fênix!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.52,0:33:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,E recupere!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.04,0:33:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A herança que seu pai Newgate \Ncertamente deixou para você,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.10,0:33:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,já que você é o legítimo herdeiro,\N sendo seu filho biológico!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.26,0:33:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi, entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.56,0:33:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.10,0:33:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu quero me vingar!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.56,0:33:30.90,Main,,0,0,0,,De Barba Negra, que matou meu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.52,0:33:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou matá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.28,0:33:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Nunca vou perdoá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.11,0:33:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Para que serve se vingar, idiota?{Acho que isso pode ficar junto, ele fala muito rápido}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não vai ganhar nem um berry!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.75,0:33:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,O que importa é o dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.46,0:33:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Você herdará a fortuna dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.08,0:33:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade, mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.45,0:33:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu, mamãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.62,0:34:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.22,0:34:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,De novo foi ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.82,0:34:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,O neto de Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que Marco e os outros \No protegeram na Grande Guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.82,0:34:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, ele pode saber sobre Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.52,0:34:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos derrotá-lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.00,0:34:30.04,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,485)\fad(433,0)}NOVO MUNDO - ILHA KARAIBARI
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.00,0:34:30.04,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(433,0)}CIDADE BUGGY
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Presidente Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.97,0:34:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Os Den Den Mushi não param \Nde tocar pedindo entregas!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.86,0:34:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Já vi, já vi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.18,0:34:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que não podem \Nobter armas de Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.70,0:34:49.32,Main,,0,0,0,,há uma grande quantidade de \Npedidos de piratas mercenários!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.32,0:34:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,O mercado militar é \Ndominado pela nossa empresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.80,0:34:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouviram?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.12,0:35:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.16,0:35:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando terminarem de comer,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.86,0:35:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,vão com tudo para os campos \Nde batalha e tragam um grande saque!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.08,0:35:15.50,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,485)\fad(285,370)}PRESIDENTE DA MENSAJERÍA BUGGY E \NPIRATA MEMBRO DO OUKA SHICHIBUKAI
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.08,0:35:15.50,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(285,370)}BUGGY, O PALHAÇO ESTRELA
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Seus atos de pirataria se tornam legais...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.80,0:35:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...quando realizados para Buggy, o Palhaço Estrela, membro do Ouka Shichibukai.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:27.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,505)\fad(433,600)}COMPANHIA PIRATA DE ENTREGAS
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:27.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,720)\fad(433,600)}MENSAJERÍA BUGGY
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.50,0:35:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim, Presidente Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.22,0:35:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hajrudin, o mercenário de \Nclasse S nos chamou...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.44,0:35:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...e disse que está renunciando.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.20,0:35:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.94,0:35:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, é só um, não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.44,0:35:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos outros quatro gigantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.62,0:35:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Os cinco estão renunciando.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.72,0:35:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,São os que mais lucro nos trazem!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.90,0:35:49.68,Main,,0,0,0,,E justo agora que temos tantos pedidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.68,0:35:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Me diga o motivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.10,0:35:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, melhor não saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.88,0:35:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.10,0:35:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.56,0:36:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não vejo o topo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.44,0:36:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Como será que Sanji e os outros escalaram isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.92,0:36:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que estão realmente lá em cima?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.44,0:36:52.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A coisa que Luffy e os outros estão montando...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.26,0:36:57.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...está escalando a perna \Ntraseira esquerda do elefante.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.41,0:37:05.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.80,0:37:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou com medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.45,0:37:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Meus braços já cansaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.20,0:37:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.16,0:37:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga isso, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está se esforçando.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.30,0:37:17.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Que fofo...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon, Kanjuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.32,0:37:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que penso nisso, \Npor que vocês queriam vir para Zou?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.84,0:37:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.48,0:37:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Devemos muito a vocês, então temos que contar tudo em algum momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas primeiro vamos nos colocar em segurança.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.22,0:37:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, quando partimos do País de Wano, \Nnosso objetivo era este, Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.90,0:37:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Queremos confirmar que \NMomonosuke está bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.12,0:37:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,...e que nosso companheiro, do qual \Nnos separamos no mar,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.90,0:37:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,o ninja Raizo, chegou aqui em segurança. {Ryu, esta NÃO a mude}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.30,0:37:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Um ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.30,0:37:48.42,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Um ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.42,0:37:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,É um ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.70,0:37:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Um ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.88,0:37:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero conhecê-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.75,0:37:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.70,0:37:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Olha lá em cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.46,0:37:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Algo está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.94,0:38:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.96,0:38:09.70,OP11 Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\NSimon\N\NTiming:\NHalee\NUmim\N\NTRADUÇÃO: \NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\N RAFAEL
